latestIgtvVideos.title: Fun with Fluid Art
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
FLUID ART FUN!

A quick easy activity to do on your own or with kids! 
Had so much fun doing this with my son that I had to do this on camera 😄 (I honestly think I enjoyed this more than him ) 

There are so many various techniques for fluid art but I have tried 2 different ones for this IGTV
(Also because I had extra paint left in the cups after the first one)

1. THE PUDDLE POUR TECHNIQUE
2. THE FLIP CUP POUR 
- Remember to cover your work table with old newspapers etc as it gets really messy.
-Try not to waste as much paint as I did in the 1st one.
- After adding the mixing medium( glue +water) to ACRYLIC paints the consistency should be like buttermilk , ie easy to pour but not too thin.
- Varnish spray your art for extra gloss and protection if you intend to hang it on your walls.
- Use gloves..I clearly forgot to 😄

Hope you enjoy this as much as I do !
HAVE FUN!!!

Ear cuffs , earrings, nail rings , palm cuffs , and super cool sunglasses. All their artisanal statement pieces are made in sterling silver, plates in 18 carat gold and all hand made in Jaipur. So very fun & funky that even Madonna loves them 😜
